title: CUSTOM DESIGNED | CONDO SPECS | KITCHEN ISLANDS | GORGEOUS LAKE VIEWS
posting_body: Italianate architectural design, condominium specifications and energy efficient features offered on 11 open, concept floor plans with 9-foot ceilings, crown molding, stained concrete flooring*, gourmet kitchens with islands, granite countertops, stainless steel appliances, natural gas ranges, built-in pantries & bookshelves, wine racks, hardwood cabinets, full-size washer and dryer connections, spacious storage closets, garden tubs and large, private patios and balconies.

In addition: resort inspired pool & spa, 24-hour fitness center, miles of hike/bike trails, all located on heavily-wooded site, overlooking huge lake, offering residents unparalleled, inspiring views.
Conveniently located near Hwy 183 and 620, only 15 mins to downtown Austin.
Large pets welcome and NO Breed Restrictions!
